title: Vampire Rodents & Ether Bunny Discography
description:
Entire discography of Vampire Rodents and Ether Bunny, both projects of electronic and industrial music composer Daniel Vahnke. Included are six full-length albums with the addition of 30 minutes of rarities taken from compilations and elsewhere. Unreleased tracks are: Lizardman, Blind Acceleration, Apocalepsy, Blue Room, Vector, Ziggurat, Schubert Trio in E Flat, Goliath and Domino Effect. The music is sample-based in the same vein as Foetus and Nine Inch Nails, with a focus on melding classical arrangements, house music rhythms, jazz composition and industrial rock. 

Albums feature a plethora of musical guests, including members of Babyland, Chemlab, Pigface, Killing Floor, Geko, 16volt, H3llb3nt, Heatmiser, Stranger Than Fiction, Ex-Voto, Fleshhouse, Front Line Assembly, SMP, Tinfed, Die Warzau, The Damage Manual, Hate Dept., Society Burning, My Life With the Thrill Kill Kult, Battery, Snark, Apparatus, The Black Heart Procession, Three Mile Pilot and Spahn Ranch.
